# Government Tender Announcement
Reissue of Request for Standing Offers: Automotive Engine Repair Services for Canadian Forces Base Trenton

## Tender Details
* **Reference Number**: WS4074909462-Doc4204056610
* **Solicitation Number**: WS4074909462
* **Amendment Number**: 0
* **Publication Date**: September 8, 2023
* **Closing Date & Time**: September 8, 2023 - 2:00 PM ET
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: N/A
* **Expected Contract End Date**: October 31, 2026
* **Status**: Cancelled

## Procurement Information
* **Procurement Category**: Service
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Variations or combinations of the above methods

## Geographic Information
* **Regions of Opportunity**: None
* **Regions of Delivery**: Quinte West

## Trade Agreements
* **Trade Agreements**: Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

* **End User Entity**: Department of National Defence (DND)
* **End User Entity Address**: 101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario K1A 0K2, Canada
* **Contact Person**: Crystal Denton (SPAC/PSPC)
* **Contact Email**: crystal.denton@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
* **Notice URL**: https://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/17399802?extsite=MTczOTk4MDJfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==

## Tender Description
This is a cancelled Request for Standing Offers (RFSO) for Automotive Engine Repair Services for Canadian Forces Base Trenton. The tender was first published on September 8, 2023, and closed on the same date at 2:00 PM ET. Due to the tender being cancelled, no further information is available. Applicants can refer to the notice URL for additional details.  Please note that trade agreements, regions of opportunity and regions of delivery are among the fields provided. However, their values are unknown. 
Therefore it is NOT recommended to participate to this cadidacy
